Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.v1_19_R3

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.v1_19_R3
Contains implementations of all version-specific code for the Spigot v1_19_R3 platform.

The main entrypoint of this package is AnimatedArchitectureSpigotSubPlatform.
